        <h3>McKenzie Bridge, OR</h3>
        <p>Surrounded by miles of hiking and mountain biking trails, the wild waters of the McKenzie River and three
          massive waterfalls, McKenzie Bridge is one of Oregon's many gems.</p>
        <p>During your trip you may notice some burn areas. These are wild fire burns from recent years.</p>
        <h3>Things to know!</h3>
        <p>
          We will be in the woods.<br>
          Dress code: Smart Casual.<br>
          Lows in the 40s, highs in the 70s.<br>
          There will be minimal cell receptions.<br>
          There are a handful of restaurants within a few miles of the venue.
